Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.31,0:00:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垠的时间停止心跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.85,0:00:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人无声息地自燃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.03,0:00:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有发觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.77,0:00:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之火笼罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.18,0:02:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 你不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.02,0:02:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.26,0:02:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.13,0:02:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体内闪动着火焰的都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.25,0:02:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之徒吞食了“存在”后消失的人类的替代物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.93,0:02:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你 “存在”已被吞食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.18,0:02:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你是残渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.78,0:02:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女一言不发地注视着惊惶失措的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后好几次都目不转睛地盯着我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.48,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那火焰般的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.30,0:02:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界异常的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邂逅了那火焰般的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.77,0:03:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃之火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.21,0:03:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.88,0:03:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经死了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.24,0:03:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被红世之徒吞食了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.08,0:03:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.04,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个怪物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.90,0:03:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是燐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当于是红世之徒的喽啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燐子收集 徒吞食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那时不是被你救了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.67,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.16,0:03:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红世之徒及燐子并不是刚刚才第一次出现在这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界上到处都有出没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.07,0:03:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的你在这遭遇之前就已经被吞食了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.06,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过火焰还很明亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.37,0:04:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似还能撑些时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 总有一天会燃尽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃尽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是作为火炬的你人间蒸发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.27,0:04:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湮灭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.71,0:04:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湮灭是指...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.43,0:04:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就好好地站在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说那些红世什么的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.88,0:04:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开了封绝嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封绝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指那火壁一样的东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.69,0:04:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确说来是指那墙壁之内的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.72,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里暂时性地从世界的潮流及因果中隔离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部发生了什么不为外界所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.55,0:05:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒吞食的并不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞食了人的“存在”之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就灰飞烟灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会留下痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.73,0:05:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看到吧 那个小火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.03,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.06,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.43,0:05:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.02,0:05:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在眼前消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.31,0:05:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是安置火炬的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.70,0:05:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“存在”消失之后世界就会失去平衡 很麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.97,0:05:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.48,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.78,0:05:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你现在正走着的堤坝弄没的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会坠落并受到冲击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.03,0:05:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.90,0:06:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把土地变成冰 渐渐消融的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到的冲击基本上感觉不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把这冰当作火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炬的存在渐渐微弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.87,0:06:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湮灭的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响已降至最低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能理解的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.22,0:06:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.08,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该做出什么样的反应呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.64,0:06:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 坂井悠二居然已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.74,0:06:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在站在这里的我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.07,0:06:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种5个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.02,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜瓜面包 吃的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那当然是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.16,0:07:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家就是这个方向的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.92,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会消失？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.26,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在做梦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让我一再重复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.18,0:07:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.18,0:07:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的居然是现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.20,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.88,0:07:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.58,0:07:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是现实？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.72,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 反应不过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事一边吃着甜瓜面包一边说出来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说那女孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 请问...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火...什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.53,0:08:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎捕并讨灭吞食“存在”的徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说安置了火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究是那一场合的弄虚作假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.48,0:08:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滥食“存在”导致世界危机这一事实是不变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.60,0:08:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱使燐子的徒看似还在这个城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听那燐子的口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.61,0:08:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是个很强大的人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不必担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外还有一个理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个秘器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.89,0:08:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么美丽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这城镇我们将得到永生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.50,0:09:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.71,0:09:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那火雾战士...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.24,0:09:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能提起破坏情趣的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.13,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只品味这美妙的时刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那种话也不要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所需要的只是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.79,0:09:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是梦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.66,0:09:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 小悠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天起得真晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.74,0:10:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 都这时候了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊 小悠居然睡过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.54,0:10:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也是一回来就睡觉去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.01,0:10:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 偶尔一次啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 果然不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈不是火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你爸爸来电话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是黄金周回不了日本了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.14,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道我已经死了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.66,0:10:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不过会变成从来就没有过小孩的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.16,0:11:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过暑假说是一定会回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其使他们伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.37,0:11:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来就没有过的情况更好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.16,0:11:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 已经不存在了吧 真正的坂井悠二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我现在在担心的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.97,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的坂井悠二会绝望 不安是没什么奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.78,0:11:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.07,0:11:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.14,0:11:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任对时间要求很严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.91,0:11:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.93,0:11:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.04,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其寻找红世之徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不如监视你来得更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.21,0:11:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个很稀有的火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.92,0:12:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫燐子什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我是“秘器”什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.74,0:12:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 记得很清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.59,0:12:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘器是指放入红世之徒所做的宝具或力量的火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.43,0:12:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝具？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炬燃尽之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容物就转入另一个火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说穿了也就是“移动宝物的仓库”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.69,0:12:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.28,0:12:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝具自己随意移动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.42,0:12:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人恐怕在你即将燃尽之时到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.91,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为火炬的秘器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我所考虑的事情都是身为坂井悠二的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残渣啊 这是当然的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.23,0:12:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.84,0:12:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 那个时候平井同学也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火好小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.88,0:13:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经所剩无几了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.93,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是是在昨天被袭击的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.44,0:13:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是被吞食了很多去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的燐子们狮子大开口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.86,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.72,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.85,0:13:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.21,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是平井同学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维持到今天已经是极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.10,0:13:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法回到原来那样子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 因为是残渣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本人已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惨什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.57,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.88,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是火炬而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.36,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.46,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.67,0:14:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 打起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.67,0:14:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么 在说自己的时候没提回不到原来的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.86,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换位思考之后 终于有了真实体会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学会消失什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.68,0:14:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道池同学有没有女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.02,0:14:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 来得真够晚的 坂井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.37,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.38,0:14:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井罚一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 平井同学也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.77,0:14:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快坐到座位上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 难得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.68,0:15:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没看平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.33,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 存在渐渐微弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.90,0:15:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遗忘...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 午饭吃什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.85,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.66,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井 你午饭有带吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.54,0:15:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去小卖部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.11,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 和池一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.05,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 池 没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.02,0:15:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行是行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.01,0:15:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.46,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班级里有那样的女生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人既然在就有呗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.07,0:16:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 那个新的补习学校的讲师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是村田他老哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.07,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要去补习学校吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.64,0:16:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 今天休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那放学后去车站前玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.92,0:16:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学也一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 随便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.72,0:16:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这么定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.93,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学 池也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然牵扯到池的话会有些反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.20,0:16:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能稍微恢复到昨天的平井同学那样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 池 再靠紧一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.94,0:16:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.92,0:16:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是不是有点碍眼了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.21,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.06,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捞东西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和池玩对打游戏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.36,0:17:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 你先和平井同学玩一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.00,0:17:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身为诱饵应该安分守己一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.17,0:17:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转来转去烦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么随便...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再怎么同情那也不过是火炬而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.82,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湮灭是不可避免的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果大家都不忘记平井同学的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.88,0:17:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用我也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到那么傻的火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.00,0:18:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.84,0:18:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 平井同学呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学啊 不是在一起的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.09,0:18:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“是吗”...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说平井同学已经...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来刚才好像出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是通关了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.95,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池 为什么这么一副漠不关心的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才我们三人还在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学她 平井同学她...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.29,0:18:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道池同学有没有女朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.05,0:18:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 坂井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.09,0:18:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是池的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.03,0:18:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 平井同学我会去找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.01,0:18:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.41,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.69,0:19:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.19,0:19:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.35,0:19:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 说了不要乱窜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个奇怪的火炬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.82,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垂死挣扎是很常有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你还在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 池说他有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.04,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 把我的那部分剪掉的话就成了和池的双人照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这景色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.86,0:20:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 所以来了这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.17,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.59,0:20:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天带池一起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 和池...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.68,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.94,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是火炬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.44,0:20:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.05,0:20:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也将如此这般消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.11,0:21:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残渣总有一天会燃尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会记得其存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会有痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说了天衣无缝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.11,0:21:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.53,0:21:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井同学存在过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.84,0:21:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜欢池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.36,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫平井由佳里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她绝对存在过 在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.94,0:21:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.27,0:21:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我叫坂井悠二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是火炬而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也是坂井悠二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.81,0:21:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是火雾战士而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.08,0:21:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上来说和火炬一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.02,0:21:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用“只是”这样的口气说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实就是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.25,0:21:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是火炬而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是火雾战士而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.28,0:21:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.16,0:21:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.95,0:22:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.89,0:22:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.25,0:22:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.61,0:22:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.63,0:22:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是火雾战士而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.82,0:22:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.86,0:22:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.76,0:22:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.51,0:22:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他的火雾战士区别时自称“贽殿遮那”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.65,0:22:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贽殿遮那？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.33,0:22:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩手中的大太刀之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.12,0:22:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贽殿遮那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.17,0:22:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就叫夏娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.59,0:22:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从此刻开始这么称呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.36,0:22:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是夏娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.42,0:22:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再只是火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.71,0:22:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不只是火炬而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.87,0:22:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是坂井悠二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.94,0:22:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.59,0:22:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字是我取的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.93,0:22:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.19,0:22:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎发灼眼的火雾战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.68,0:22:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了夏娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.02,0:24:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然出现在学校的燐子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.68,0:24:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于现身的红世之王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.67,0:24:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法利亚格尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.21,0:24:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 城市中另一位火雾战士的影子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.37,0:24:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.48,0:24:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火炬与火雾战士
